Representatives of all peoples and religions in Azerbaijan live as a comfortable family, enjoy all rights.
In Azerbaijan, interethnic, inter-religious relations will develop on this solid foundation and our unity, our strength will increase.
Our society has very solid supports. These stands are based on history, deep spirituality, mutual understanding, mutual support.
Establishing religious-state relations on the proper ground is important for every state, especially for younger states.
Azerbaijan is a multinational, multi-confessional state. This is our great fortune. We protect and protect this wealth.
The initiatives of the great leader Heydar Aliyev in this area are highly appreciated by the people.
About 2,000 mosques have been built in Azerbaijan during the years of independence.
Nearly 140 mosques were built during the last 10 years and 80 mosques were repaired.
Religious buildings and temples of other religions are being repaired and constructed.
We have to make sure that the next generation after us will be educated in the spirit of patriotism in the national spirit.
National moral values ​​should be the basis for future generations. Because our state is based on national values.
Everyone can see how successful inter-religious and inter-state relations can be observed in Azerbaijan.
Multiculturalism has many positive experiences, positive signs and addresses in the world. One of them is Azerbaijan.

The day of the "human-action" is a commemoration of what Zayid loved, and we will establish our country as the international capital for good work.
